high_descs: Walk toward the window, then hang a right and walk up to the counter.
Pick up the large metal knife off of the counter.
Turn right and walk forward, then turn left to face the sink.
Put the large metal knife in the sink and turn on the water, after a couple seconds turn the water off and remove the now clean knife.
Turn left and walk forward, then turn left and walk over to the counter and turn left again.
Open the last drawer on your right and put the large clean knife inside the drawer, then close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put a large clean knife in a drawer.

high_descs: Go forward and then turn right to face the sink.
Pick up the knife from the sink.
Move to the right to face the sink basin.
Wash the knife in the sink basin.
Turn around and go to the counter in front of you, then turn left to face the drawer at the end of the counter.
Put the knife in the drawer at the end of the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean knife in the drawer.

high_descs: Walk to the left side of the sink that's in front of you to the right and turn right to face it when you get there and take a step towards it.
Pick up the yellow handled knife that's in front of you.
Take a a step to your right.
Wash the knife in the sink and then pick it back up and shut off the water.
Turn around and walk to the counter then turn left and take a small step back.
Open the drawer to the right of you that's on the end and put the knife in there then close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean knife in the drawer.
